 (52017007), <a href="/web/20180712203525/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_SNOMEDCT_US_CUI=C0010210&amp;fLockTerm=Counseling">Counseling</a>
 (129441002), <a href="/web/20180712203525/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_SNOMEDCT_US_CUI=C0010210&amp;fLockTerm=Counseling">Counseling</a>
 (409063005), <a href="/web/20180712203525/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_SNOMEDCT_US_CUI=C0009373&amp;fLockTerm=Disorder+of+colon">Disorder of colon</a>
 (128524007), <a href="/web/20180712203525/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_SNOMEDCT_US_CUI=C0034882&amp;fLockTerm=Disorder+of+rectum">Disorder of rectum</a>
 (5964004), <a href="/web/20180712203525/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_SNOMEDCT_US_CUI=C0553741&amp;fLockTerm=Fluid+balance+regulation">Fluid balance regulation</a>
 (276026009), <a href="/web/20180712203525/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_SNOMEDCT_US_CUI=C0021889&amp;fLockTerm=Intraoperative+care">Intraoperative care</a>
