 (17102003), <a href="/web/20180712203525/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_SNOMEDCT_US_CUI=C2937349&amp;fLockTerm=Nutrition+therapy">Nutrition therapy</a>
 (386373004), <a href="/web/20180712203525/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_SNOMEDCT_US_CUI=C0038898&amp;fLockTerm=Operative+procedure+on+digestive+system">Operative procedure on digestive system</a>
 (107907001), <a href="/web/20180712203525/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_SNOMEDCT_US_CUI=C0002766&amp;fLockTerm=Pain+management">Pain management</a>
